    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liminal Death is a first person psychological horror game with liminal space environments where  you will expirience what will happened when someone falls in comma and gets trap  inbetween worlds, you will have to fight through a maze and find your path to get to the other side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267360/extras/452d4bf292c3b1e1384dffa9a379fb61.poster.avif?t=1730102423\" width=522 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267360/extras/452d4bf292c3b1e1384dffa9a379fb61.webm?t=1730102423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267360/extras/452d4bf292c3b1e1384dffa9a379fb61.mp4?t=1730102423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Ojiisan, a 52 years old woman who gets a heart attack while she is at her garden at home. She soon finds himself in trouble as her sould gets trap inbetween worlds full of trap souls and horror after she faals into comma, if she finds her path back to her body she might live! would he make it through to the other side?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267360/extras/f1327477f6cefe6bdaec0255253fb521.poster.avif?t=1730102423\" width=522 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267360/extras/f1327477f6cefe6bdaec0255253fb521.webm?t=1730102423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267360/extras/f1327477f6cefe6bdaec0255253fb521.mp4?t=1730102423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game it has retro graphics with a first person camara perspective with no combat, but you still need to be carefull on what you will find in the inbetween worlds because you will never come back from the coma.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
